14
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:11,000
Weiwan.

15
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:11,880
Fantastic!

16
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:24,240
- Bravo!
- Amazing!

17
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,440
Excellent!

18
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:38,080
Great.

19
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:40,800
- Fantastic.
- It's worth the trip.

20
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:47,080
Well done.

21
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,560
